metadata.name: Stand with Ukraine
metadata.description:
Of Ukrainian heritage, acclaimed actress Tasya Teles refuses to be silenced about the destructive war in the Ukraine. Equipped with a creative tour de force, this iconic NFT captures a moment in time where people all over the world rise up to speak against violence, war, and the ruinous humanitarian consequences for the world at large. 

Shot by acclaimed photographer Peter Ruprecht, produced by Shannon Shiang, with body painting by Adrián Castro Gómez.  

We will not be silenced.
